    "description": "Welcome to Seas of Hydra! Sent to a watery world, the player, Hadwritz Yothich, fishes off of a friendly sea turtle in exchange for feeding it. Looks like you have some work to do!<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\nUse your trusty rod to scavenge the seas for various fish, all with their own behaviors and quirks. Some may be quick, slow, consistent, or random. All you need to do is hook them to find out.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\nYour new turtle friend doesn't eat fish, but luckily someone does. A seagull has set up shop on his reliable sea craft. He will willingly trade your fish for upgrades, accessories, and most importantly, turtle food. You’ll need it as your turtle companion grows ever hungrier.<br />\r\n\t<br />\r\nFind many unique fish, upgrade your rod, and see how long you can last in this relaxing fishing game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game was developed and produced entirely by an aspiring team of high school students in a little over half a year. Any support helps us achieve our dreams of becoming successful game developers.",
